---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="下班後理財 | 白天努力生活，晚上規劃自由。"
    description="下班後理財是您最值得信賴的資產管理夥伴，提供專業、私密、直觀的資產追蹤工具。一站式管理您的全球資產。"
>
    <main
        class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24 max-w-7xl relative z-10 min-h-screen"
    >
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <header class="text-center space-y-8 mb-32 animate-fade-in-down">
            <div
                class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4"
            >
                專業資產追蹤工具
            </div>
            <h1
                class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight"
            >
                <span
                    class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600"
                    >掌握財富，開啟自由人生</span
                >
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-700 tracking-wide mt-4"
            >
                白天努力生活，晚上規劃自由。
            </p>
            <p
                class="text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed mt-6"
            >
                整合現金、股票與房地產，即時掌握您的資產淨值與長期成長趨勢。
            </p>

            <!-- Bento Grid Section -->
            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full"
            >
                <!-- Assets Manager: Main Feature -->
                <a
                    href="/assets-manager"
                    class="group relative md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[400px]"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50/50 to-indigo-50/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div
                            class="bg-blue-600 text-white w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-blue-200"
                        >
                            💰
                        </div>
                        <h2
                            class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight"
                        >
                            資產總覽儀表板
                        </h2>
                        <p
                            class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md"
                        >
                            整合您的現金、股票與房地產，一眼掌握全球資產淨值與分佈。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3 text-blue-600 font-bold"
                    >
                        立即開始管理 <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="20"
                            height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2.5"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform"
                            ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                            ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                            ></polyline></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                </a>

                <!-- Compound Interest Calculator -->
                <a
                    href="/compound-interest"
                    class="group relative bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-6 border border-blue-500/30"
                        >
                            📈
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
                            複利效應試算
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            見證時間的力量，計算您的長期投資收益與財富翻倍速度。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <span
                        class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-sm mt-6 flex items-center gap-2"
                    >
                        見證複利 <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="16"
                            height="16"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                            ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                            ></polyline></svg
                        >
                    </span>
                </a>

                <!-- Coast FIRE & Rent vs Buy in a smaller grid or row -->
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:col-span-3"
                >
                    <!-- Coast FIRE Calculator -->
                    <a
                        href="/coast-fire"
                        class="group relative bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50/50 to-purple-50/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-6"
                            >
                                🔥
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                                Coast FIRE 計算
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                計算何時能停止主動儲蓄，讓資產複利帶您抵達退休終點。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="text-indigo-600 font-bold text-sm mt-6 flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            探索未來 <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                width="16"
                                height="16"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                                ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                                ></polyline></svg
                            >
                        </span>
                    </a>

                    <!-- Rent vs Buy -->
                    <a
                        href="/rent-vs-buy"
                        class="group relative bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50/50 to-teal-50/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-6"
                            >
                                🏠
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                                買房 vs 租房
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                考量稅率、投報率與維護成本，幫您做出最明智的居住決策。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="text-emerald-600 font-bold text-sm mt-6 flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            開始試算 <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                width="16"
                                height="16"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                                ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                                ></polyline></svg
                            >
                        </span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="pt-16 flex items-center justify-center gap-8 grayscale opacity-50"
            >
                <div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase">
                    Supported Assets
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <span class="text-2xl" title="Cash">💰</span>
                    <span class="text-2xl" title="Stock">📈</span>
                    <span class="text-2xl" title="Real Estate">🏠</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Social Proof / Trust -->
        <div class="py-20 border-y border-slate-100 mb-32">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center">
                <div>
                    <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                        100%
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="text-slate-500 font-medium tracking-wide text-sm"
                    >
                        數據隱私
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                        Real-time
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="text-slate-500 font-medium tracking-wide text-sm"
                    >
                        即時匯率更新
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                        Free
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="text-slate-500 font-medium tracking-wide text-sm"
                    >
                        開源且永久免費
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <article id="features" class="space-y-32 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <section class="text-center space-y-16">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900">
                        強大功能，極簡體驗
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg">
                        為您打造的現代財務儀表板
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
                    <div
                        class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="text-4xl mb-6 bg-blue-50 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >
                            🔒
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
                            極致隱私安全
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            您的財務數據僅儲存在您的瀏覽器 (Local
                            Storage)，我們不收集、不上傳任何個人資料。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="text-4xl mb-6 bg-purple-50 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:bg-purple-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >
                            🌍
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
                            全球匯率整合
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            即時串接國際匯率
                            API，支持多國貨幣。自動換算為您的本幣價值，掌握全球佈局。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="text-4xl mb-6 bg-emerald-50 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl group-hover:bg-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >
                            📊
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
                            動態資產估值
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            針對不同資產類型提供專屬計算模型。股票股數、外幣存款都能精準轉換為即時價值。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Educational Content (Shifted for marketing) -->
            <section
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center bg-slate-50 rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-20 overflow-hidden relative"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-200 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-20 -mr-20 -mt-20"
                >
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-8 relative z-10">
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight"
                    >
                        掌握淨資產，<br /><span class="text-blue-600"
                            >規劃財務自由的第一步</span
                        >
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600">
                        <p class="leading-relaxed">
                            淨資產是衡量個人財務健康狀況最核心的指標。它的計算公式非常簡單：<strong
                                >總資產 (Assets) - 總負債 (Liabilities) = 淨資產</strong
                            >。
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-900 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6 py-2 bg-blue-50/50 rounded-r-xl"
                        >
                            Asset Manager
                            協助您客觀地檢視財富增長，並及早發現潛在的財務風險。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <a
                        href="/assets-manager"
                        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-blue-600 hover:gap-4 transition-all"
                    >
                        進入資產管理工具 <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="20"
                            height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"
                            ></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"
                            ></polyline></svg
                        >
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="relative group">
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl rotate-3 opacity-10 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100"
                    >
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="h-4 bg-slate-100 rounded w-3/4"></div>
                            <div class="h-4 bg-slate-100 rounded w-1/2"></div>
                            <div
                                class="h-32 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center"
                            >
                                <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600"
                                    >$ Net Worth</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- FAQ -->
            <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-12 pb-20">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center">
                    常見問題
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <details
                        class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <summary
                            class="list-none cursor-pointer font-bold text-slate-900 flex justify-between items-center"
                        >
                            Q: 我的財務數據會被傳送到伺服器嗎？
                            <span
                                class="text-blue-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
                                >▼</span
                            >
                        </summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            A:
                            完全不會。「下班後理財」是一個純前端運作的應用程式
                            (Client-side
                            App)。所有的資料都加密儲存在您裝置的瀏覽器資料庫中，即使我們也無法看見您的資產狀況。
                        </p>
                    </details>
                    <details
                        class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <summary
                            class="list-none cursor-pointer font-bold text-slate-900 flex justify-between items-center"
                        >
                            Q: 匯率是即時的嗎？
                            <span
                                class="text-blue-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
                                >▼</span
                            >
                        </summary>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            A: 是的，系統每 5 分鐘會自動從國際匯率 API
                            獲取最新的匯率資訊。如果您的裝置處於離線狀態，系統會自動使用上一次更新的匯率進行計算。
                        </p>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </section>
        </article>

        <footer
            class="text-center text-slate-400 text-sm py-12 border-t border-slate-100 mt-20"
        >
            <p>
                © 2026 下班後理財. Data stored locally. Open sourced on GitHub.
            </p>
        </footer>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
    .animate-fade-in-down {
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    }
    html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
</style>
